dct_title_s: Pacific Coast from Point Pinos to Bodega Head, California
dct_description_sm: from a trigonometrical survey under the direction of A.D. Bache, Superintendent of the Survey of the Coast of the United States.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights; depths shown by soundings and isolines.
"Electrotype copy no. 1 by G. Mathiot, U.S.C.S."
Oriented with north toward upper right.
